        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1199957/pexels-photo-1199957.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" class="card-img-top" alt="Menu 1">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Burger 1</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Savor a symphony of flavors with our signature Burger! A juicy cheesy patty, chargrilled to perfection, is nestled between toasted buns. Melted  adds creamy richness, while toppings create a delightful textural contrast. A drizzle of our house-made  ties it all together for an unforgettable burger experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2147491/pexels-photo-2147491.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" class="card-img-top" alt="Menu 2">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Pizza</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Indulge in a slice of heaven with our Peri Peri Pizza! Our Pan crust is hand-tossed and baked to a golden crisp, holding up a symphony of White Sauce and melty Cheese Blend goodness. Savor  bursting with flavor, all coming together in a single, unforgettable bite.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Add more cards as needed -->
        </div>
